column3:
Kinepin brand's cuticle nipper is made from stainless steel and it's metal jaw with sharp edges can easily grasp and cut away excessive skin around the cuticle. 


This cuticle nippers are surgical-quality with stainless steel tip. Its sharp blades can cut even the tiniest cuticle every time without pulling or tugging.
Made from premium brushed stainless steel to retain sharpness for a very long period of time. You'll get the precision cut every time you use it!
It is easy to clean and store.

2 Inch X 0.50 Inch Stainless Steel Angle Bracket
column3:
Fixit.com.bd's angle bracket  is an L-shaped fastener mainly used to join two flat surfaces firmly at a 90 degree angle.

Premium grade stainless steel make our angle brackets durable rust and corrosion free.
Specially designed with exactly 90 degrees.
Widely used in home and factory areas mainly to join a wooden shelf to a wall or to join two furniture parts together.
You can easily install it with screws and washers.

Angle Brackets are also called corner braces corner bracket braces shelf brackets or L brackets.

column3:
Fixit.com.bd brand's nail cutter mainly designed to trim fingernails toenails and hangnails. 

ERGONOMIC: Unique handle design allows the nail clippers to cradle fingers making it easier to control and delivering a more confident clip every time.
EFFORTLESS: Sharpened stainless steel blades cut thick nails smoothly and easily with no need for filing preventing nail and the toenails splitting. It can be used also to clean dirt out from under the nails and to allow rough edges of nails to be manicured.
EXQUISITE:It is a beautifully designed nail cutter set which can be a very good choice as a  gift item.
